'''2,4,5-三羟基肉桂酸'''（{{lang-en|2,4,5-Trihydroxycinnamic acid}}）是一种[[天然产物|天然的]][[羟基肉桂酸|羟基肉桂酸]]化合物，化学式[[C9H8O5|C<sub>9</sub>H<sub>8</sub>O<sub>5</sub>]]，存在[[顺反异构|顺反异构]]体，发现于[[博士茶|博士茶]]（学名：''Aspalathus linearis''）<ref>{{cite journal | doi = 10.1016/S0031-9422(00)86894-6| title = Phenolic metabolites from rooibos tea (Aspalathus linearis)| url = https://archive.org/details/sim_phytochemistry_1994-04_35_6/page/1559| journal = Phytochemistry| volume = 35| issue = 6| pages = 1559| year = 1994| last1 = Rabe| first1 = Charlene| last2 = Steenkamp| first2 = Jacobus A.| last3 = Joubert| first3 = Elizabeth| last4 = Burger| first4 = Johann F.W.| last5 = Ferreira| first5 = Daneel}}</ref>、[[东方泽泻|东方泽泻]]（学名：''Alisma orientale''）<ref>{{cite journal | pmid=22816308| year=2012| last1=Zhao| first1=M| title=Cis-aconitic anhydride ethyl ester and phenolic compounds from the seeds of Alisma orientale| journal=Natural Product Communications| volume=7| issue=6| pages=785–7| last2=Chen| first2=J. Y.| last3=Xu| first3=L. J.| last4=Goedecke| first4=T| last5=Zhang| first5=X. Q.| last6=Duan| first6=J. A.| last7=Che| first7=C. T.| doi=10.1177/1934578X1200700624| s2cid=21479738| doi-access=free}}</ref>等植物中。

